(1305, 340, 'news_content', '<div class=\"html-div xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x78zum5 x1eb86dx\">\r\n<div class=\"html-div xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl xeuugli x1vjfegm\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"html-div xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x78zum5 xh8yej3\" role=\"presentation\">\r\n<div class=\"x1cy8zhl x78zum5 xdt5ytf x193iq5w x1n2onr6 x1kxipp6\">\r\n<div class=\"x78zum5 xh8yej3\" role=\"none\">\r\n<div class=\"html-div xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x6ikm8r x10wlt62\">\r\n<div class=\"html-div xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak x14ctfv x13sv91t x6ikm8r x10wlt62 xerhiuh x1pn3fxy x10zy8in xm9bcq3 x1n2onr6 x1vjfegm x1k4qllp x1mzt3pk x13faqbe x1xr0vuk x1jm4cbz x114wg8e xrrpcnn x14rx4xb x13fuv20 x18b5jzi x1q0q8m5 x1t7ytsu x19livfd x1h2krnu x3p3xfz xet2kk3 xaymx6s x1lu5o8o x1ou5ly4 xofb2d2\" role=\"presentation\">\r\n<div class=\"html-div xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x1gslohp x14z9mp x12nagc x1lziwak x1yc453h x126k92a x18lvrbx\" dir=\"auto\">To strengthen students’ awareness of online safety issues and enhance their critical thinking skills, MBGSNHS held its Safer Internet Day 2026 celebration. Led by Homeroom advisers and Values Education teachers under the guidance of Ma\'am Reann Vee Gragasin, Guidance Advocate and Child Protection Policy Coordinator; Sir Valentin Remperas, Values Education Head Teacher and Guidance Designate; and supported by Ma\'am Jayvee De Ocampo, Values Education Coordinator, with the active participation of selected learners, the event successfully commenced on February 10, 2026.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"html-div xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x1h91t0o xkh2ocl x78zum5 xdt5ytf x13a6bvl x193iq5w x1iyjqo2 x1eb86dx\" role=\"presentation\">\r\n<div class=\"html-div xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x1r8uery x1iyjqo2\" role=