(1313, 341, 'news_content', 'the official student publication of Leandro G. Japos National High School continues to raise Banaybanay district\'s banner in the RSPC stage winning the following awards in the recent RSPC School Paper Contest: 𝐅𝐈𝐑𝐒𝐓 𝐏𝐋𝐀𝐂𝐄 Editorial Section 𝐅𝐈𝐑𝐒𝐓 𝐏𝐋𝐀𝐂𝐄 Features Section 𝐅𝐎𝐔𝐑𝐓𝐇 𝐏𝐋𝐀𝐂𝐄 Science and Technology Section 𝐍𝐈𝐍𝐓𝐇 𝐏𝐋𝐀𝐂𝐄 Layout and Page Design The Tributary will be representing the Schools Division of Davao Oriental and Region XI in the upcoming National Schools Press Conference to be held at Ormoc City this April 2026. #TheTributary2026 #NSPC2026 See less'),
