(1321, 346, 'news_content', '<div class=\"html-div xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x78zum5 x1eb86dx\">\r\n<div class=\"html-div xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl xeuugli x1vjfegm\">\r\n<div class=\"html-div xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x78zum5 xh8yej3\" role=\"presentation\">\r\n<div class=\"x1cy8zhl x78zum5 xdt5ytf x193iq5w x1n2onr6 x1kxipp6\">\r\n<div class=\"x78zum5 xh8yej3\" role=\"none\">\r\n<div class=\"html-div xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x6ikm8r x10wlt62\">\r\n<div class=\"html-div xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak x14ctfv x13sv91t x6ikm8r x10wlt62 xerhiuh x1pn3fxy x10zy8in xm9bcq3 x1n2onr6 x1vjfegm x1k4qllp x1mzt3pk x13faqbe x1xr0vuk x1jm4cbz x114wg8e xrrpcnn x14rx4xb x13fuv20 x18b5jzi x1q0q8m5 x1t7ytsu x19livfd x1h2krnu x3p3xfz xet2kk3 xaymx6s x1lu5o8o x1ou5ly4 xofb2d2\" role=\"presentation\">\r\n<div class=\"html-div xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x1gslohp x14z9mp x12nagc x1lziwak x1yc453h x126k92a x18lvrbx\" dir=\"auto\">\r\n<div class=\"x78zum5 xdt5ytf x1iyjqo2 xhc7eg\">\r\n<div class=\"x9f619 x1ja2u2z __fb-light-mode x1xsqp64 x18d0r48 x78zum5 x1r8uery xdt5ytf x1iyjqo2 xmz0i5r x6ikm8r x10wlt62 x1n2onr6\">\r\n<div class=\"x78zum5 xdt5ytf x1iyjqo2 x5yr21d\">\r\n<div class=\"x78zum5 xdt5ytf x1iyjqo2 x5yr21d\">\r\n<div class=\"x1gp6l83 x18b5jzi x1alpsbp x148vw1v x1t7ytsu xyumdvf x78zum5 xdt5ytf x1iyjqo2 x6ikm8r x10wlt62\" role=\"grid\" aria-label=\"Messages in conversation titled MBGSNHS OJT\">\r\n<div class=\"x1qjc9v5 x9f619 xdl72j9 x2lwn1j xeuugli x1n2onr6 x78zum5 xdt5ytf x1iyjqo2 xs83m0k x6ikm8r x10wlt62 x1ja2u2z\">\r\n<div class=\"x78zum5 xdt5ytf x1iyjqo2 x6ikm8r x1odjw0f x8du1vd x16o0dkt\" role=\"none\">\r\n<div class=\"x78zum5 xdt5ytf x1iyjqo2 x2lah0s xl56j7k x121v3j4\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"x78zum5 xdt5ytf\" data-virtualized=\"false\">\r\n<div class=\"x9f619 x1n2onr6 x1ja2u2z\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"__fb-light-mode x1n2onr6\" role=\"row\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"x78zum5 xdt5ytf x1n2onr6\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"gridcell\" data-release-focus-from=\"CLICK\" data-scope=\"messages_table\">\r\n<div class=\"html-div xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x78zum5 x1eb86dx\">\r\n<div class=\"html-div xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl xeuugli x1vjfegm\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"html-div xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x78zum5 xh8yej3\" role=\"presentation\">\r\n<div class=\"x1cy8zhl x78zum5 xdt5ytf x193iq5w x1n2onr6 x1kxipp6\">\r\n<div class=\"x78zum5 xh8yej3\" role=\"none\">\r\n<div class=\"html-div xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x6ikm8r x10wlt62\">\r\n<div class=\"html-div xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak x14ctfv x13sv91t x6ikm8r x10wlt62 xerhiuh x1pn3fxy x10zy8in xm9bcq3 x1n2onr6 x1vjfegm x1k4qllp x1mzt3pk x13faqbe x1xr0vuk x1jm4cbz x114wg8e xrrpcnn x14rx4xb x13fuv20 x18b5jzi x1q0q8m5 x1t7ytsu x19livfd x1h2krnu x3p3xfz xet2kk3 xaymx6s x1lu5o8o x1ou5ly4 xofb2d2\" role=\"presentation\">\r\n<div class=\"html-div xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x1gslohp x14z9mp x12nagc x1lziwak x1yc453h x126k92a x18lvrbx\" dir=\"auto\">Young Leaders Rise: Banaybanay District conducts SELG and SSLG Elections In a meaningful gathering of emerging leaders, Banaybanay District successfully conducted its Supreme Elementary Learner Government (SELG) and Supreme Secondary Learner Government (SSLG) Elections, bringing together student leaders and dedicated teacher-advisers from various schools across the district. The program formally began with a warm welcome from District SELG Coordinator, Precious N. Quindoyos, who acknowledged the presence of the participants and emphasized the importance of student leadership in strengthening school communities. The presentation of the Rationale of the Activity by SSLG District Coordinator, Philip Deleguera, highlighted the purpose of the election and its role in empowering learners to take active participation in governance and service.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"html-div xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x1h91t0o xkh2ocl x78zum5 xdt5ytf x13a6bvl x193iq5w x1iyjqo2 x1eb86dx\" role=\"presentation\">\r\n<div class=\"html-div xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x1r8uery x1iyjqo2\" role=\"presentation\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"xuk3077 x57kliw x78zum5 x6prxxf xz9dl7a xsag5q8\" role=\"group\" aria-label=\"Thread composer\">\r\n<div class=\"x1iyjqo2 xw2csxc x1n2onr6\">\r\n<div class=\"x78zum5 x1iyjqo2 x6q2ic0\">\r\n<div class=\"x16sw7j7 x12ol6y4 x180vkcf x1khw62d x709u02 x9f619 xlai7qp x1iyjqo2 xeuugli\">\r\n<div class=\"x78zum5 x13a6bvl\">\r\n<div class=\"x78zum5 x1iyjqo2 x1xmf6yo x1e56ztr xbmvrgn x1diwwjn xeuugli x1n2onr6\">\r\n<div class=\"xzsf02u x1a2a7pz x1n2onr6 x14wi4xw x1iyjqo2 x19gmnou xisnujt xeuugli x1odjw0f notranslate\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"textbox\" contenteditable=\"true\" spellcheck=\"true\" aria-describedby=\"_r_37_\" aria-label=\"Message\" aria-placeholder=\"Aa\" data-lexical-editor=\"true\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>'),
