(1329, 347, 'news_content', 'Philippines 2026 To strengthen students’ awareness of online safety issues and enhance their critical thinking skills, MBGSNHS held its Safer Internet Day 2026 celebration. Led by Homeroom advisers and Values Education teachers under the guidance of Ma\'am Reann Vee Gragasin, Guidance Advocate and Child Protection Policy Coordinator; Sir Valentin Remperas, Values Education Head Teacher and Guidance Designate; and supported by Ma\'am Jayvee De Ocampo, Values Education Coordinator, with the active participation of selected learners, the event successfully commenced on February 10, 2026.'),
