(1566, 383, 'news_content', '<div class=\"x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\r\n<div dir=\"auto\"><span class=\"html-span xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x3nfvp2 x1j61x8r x1fcty0u xdj266r xat24cr xm2jcoa x1mpyi22 xxymvpz xlup9mm x1kky2od\"><strong>Written by</strong>: </span>Junellen Bianca F. Alonso</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">The Banaybanay District Star Scouts and Twinklers proudly represented the district during the 19th Councilwide Star Holiday and Twinklers’ Playday held in Baganga, Davao Oriental on March 13–15, 2026.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">Accompanied by six dedicated adult leaders from Looc Pt. Linao Elementary School and Banaybanay Central Elementary School, the young scouts actively participated in the different activities prepared for the event. Their enthusiasm, teamwork, and scouting spirit did not only make their participation meaningful but also brought pride and honor to the district.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">The Banaybanay District delegates achieved remarkable success as they garnered the following recognitions:</div>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li dir=\"auto\">Respectful Cluster Award</li>\r\n 	<li dir=\"auto\">1st Place – Treasure Hunt</li>\r\n 	<li dir=\"auto\">2nd Place – Fantasy Night Contest</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">These achievements highlighted the scouts’ discipline, creativity, cooperation, and strong sense of camaraderie, making Banaybanay District proud of their outstanding performance.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">The delegation would like to express their heartfelt gratitude to Vanessa T. Duot, Public Schools District Supervisor, for her continued support to scouting activities. Special thanks are also extended to Lemuel Ian M. Larcia for providing transportation for the participants.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">Appreciation is likewise given to Marivic I. Aranayado, District Field Adviser, and to the supportive parents for entrusting their daughters to the care and guidance of the scout leaders.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">Indeed, the event was not only a venue for fun and adventure but also a meaningful opportunity for the young scouts to develop leadership, friendship, and the true spirit of scouting.</div>\r\n</div>'),
